About me Hi there! I am Natasya Nadhira, currently a final-year student at Universiti Teknologi Malaysia (UTM). I will graduate in October 2024 with a Bachelor of Computer Science (Graphics and Multimedia Software) with Honours. I have a passion for learning and exploring new technologies. It’s incredibly fulfilling for me to discover tools that can enhance my development process. Currently, I specialize in computer graphics-related domain throughout my studies. I’ve delved into various areas including 3D graphics rendering pipelines, game development, web development, mobile development, Augmented Reality (AR), Virtual Reality (VR), Mixed Reality (MR), Computer Vision, Artificial Intelligence (AI), and Machine Learning (ML).
